<quantity box="[1217,1278,512,536]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" unit="m" value="40.0">40 m</quantity>
), it appears to be more common in the 
<collectingCountry box="[446,575,548,573]" name="Philippines" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Philippines</collectingCountry>
